     function InitSlider() {
 
         if (Slides != null)
             $(Slides).each(function () {
                 $("<img/>")[0].src = this;
             });
 
         GoSlide(0, 0);
 
     }
 
     function GoSlide(Index, Vitesse) {
 
         $("#Slider span.Filtre").animate({ "background-color": "rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)" }, Vitesse, function () {
 
             $("#Slider").css({ "background": "#232323" });
 
             if (Slides != null)
                 if (Slides.length > Index)
                     if (Slides[Index] != null)
                         $("#Slider")
                             .css({ "background": "url('" + Slides[Index] + "') no-repeat #FFFFFF" })
                             .css({ "background-position": "center center" })
                             .css({ "-webkit-background-size": "cover" })
                             .css({ "background-size": "cover" });
 
             $("#Slider span.Filtre span.Slogan").html("");
 
             if (Slogans != null)
                 if (Slogans.length > Index)
                     if (Slogans[Index] != null)
                         $("#Slider span.Filtre span.Slogan").html(Slogans[Index]);
 
             $("#Slider").removeAttr("href");
 
             if (Liens != null)
                 if (Liens.length > Index)
                     if (Liens[Index] != null)
                         $("#Slider").attr("href", Liens[Index]);
 
             $("#Slider span.Filtre").animate({ "background-color": "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)" }, Vitesse, function () {
 
                 if (Slides != null)
                     if (Slides.length > Index + 1) {
 
                         setTimeout(function () { GoSlide(Index + 1, 500); }, 10000);
                         return;
 
                     }
 
                 setTimeout(function () { GoSlide(0, 500); }, 10000);
 
             });
 
         });
 
     }
       </script>
